XF1ZXN0UmV2aWV3Q29tbWVudDQ1MDk5NjE0NA==", "bodyText": "I feel like we can use a better example than alluxio.heartbeat. Maybe alluxio.underfs? Its something more users might understand/know about.\nJust a suggestion", "url": "https://github.com/Alluxio/alluxio/pull/11724#discussion_r450996144", "createdAt": "2020-07-07T16:34:23Z", "author": {"login": "ZacBlanco"}, "path": "docs/en/operation/Basic-Logging.md", "diffHunk": "@@ -110,6 +110,24 @@ And the following command returns the log level of the class `alluxio.heartbeat.\n $ ./bin/alluxio logLevel --logName=alluxio.heartbeat.HeartbeatContext --target=workers\n ```\n \n+You can also update the log level at a package level.\n+For example, you can update the log level of all classes in `alluxio.heartbeat` package with the following command:\n+```console\n+$ ./bin/alluxio logLevel --logName=alluxio.heartbeat --target=workers --level=DEBUG\n+```\n+This works because log4j loggers will inherit the log level from their ancestors.\n+In this case `alluxio.heartbeat.HeartbeatContext` inherits the log level if it is set on `alluxio.heartbeat`.", "state": "SUBMITTED", "replyTo": null, "originalCommit": {"oid": "0db929534502e596337f95a31ecba01040dc6911"}, "originalPosition": 10}]}}, {"__typename": "PullRequestReview", "id": "MDE3OlB1bGxSZXF1ZXN0UmV2aWV3NDQ0MDYyOTc1", "url": "https://github.com/Alluxio/alluxio/pull/11724#pullrequestreview-444062975", "createdAt": "2020-07-07T16:34:25Z", "commit": {"oid": "0db929534502e596337f95a31ecba01040dc6911"}, "state": "APPROVED", "comments": {"totalCount": 0, "pageInfo": {"startCursor": null, "endCursor": null, "hasNextPage": false, "hasPreviousPage": false}, "nodes": []}}, {"__typename": "PullRequestCommit", "commit": {"oid": "4c1cb96ee6bcb3e6113990561dca07ab07639110", "author": {"user": {"login": "jiacheliu3", "name": "Jiacheng Liu"}}, "url": "https://github.com/Alluxio/alluxio/commit/4c1cb96ee6bcb3e6113990561dca07ab07639110", "committedDate": "2020-07-13T07:12:45Z", "message": "resolve c